{"arkId":"cl010117230","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010117230","modified ":"2025-11-20","title":"Rouleau: Sur le fleuve, le jour de la f\u00eate de Qingming (Qingming shangue tu \u6e05\u660e\u4e0a\u6cb3\u5716)","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Rouleau: Sur le fleuve, le jour de la f\u00eate de Qingming (Qingming shangue tu \u6e05\u660e\u4e0a\u6cb3\u5716)"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : \u00e9poque Qianlong = Kien . Iung =  Kienlong = KianLong (1736-1795) (Chine-\u003Edynastie Qing (1644-1911))\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1768","currentLocation":"non expos\u00e9","room":"","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1768,"endYear":"","imprecision":"","text":"2e moiti\u00e9 du XVIIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Yao Wenhan \u59da\u6587\u701a","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"Peintre","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"TH 284","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"dessin, pastel ; art du livre : miniature, enluminure","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Ce rouleau du XVIIIe si\u00e8cle est une version miniature r\u00e9interpr\u00e9t\u00e9e du Qingming shanghe tu (Sur le fleuve, le jour de la f\u00eate de Qingming) de Zhang Zeduan \u5f35\u64c7\u7aef (1085-1145), l\u2019une des oeuvres les plus c\u00e9l\u00e8bres de l\u2019histoire de l\u2019art chinois. Command\u00e9e par l\u0027empereur Qianlong en personne \u00e0 Yao Wenhan, peintre de la cour, elle fut achev\u00e9e en 1768, puis remont\u00e9e pour \u00eatre r\u00e9duite l\u0027ann\u00e9e suivante afin de pouvoir \u00eatre rang\u00e9e dans un petit coffret, et enfin, deux ans plus tard, a \u00e9t\u00e9 rajout\u00e9e la calligraphie d\u0027un po\u00e8me compos\u00e9 par Qianlong. C\u0027est donc au seul plaisir imp\u00e9rial qu\u0027\u00e9tait destin\u00e9 ce petit rouleau d\u0027une si grande finesse. L\u0027illustration si vivante des sc\u00e8nes se succ\u00e9dant pendant un jour de f\u00eate refl\u00e8te la prosp\u00e9rit\u00e9 dans laquelle vivent ses sujets, r\u00e9sultat d\u0027une sage et juste gouvernance.","inscriptions":"Etiquette : \r ; 284\r ; \u0022465\u0022 (\u00e9tiquette imprim\u00e9e)","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"16,2","displayDimension":"16,2 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Longueur","value":"431","displayDimension":"431 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : papier\r\nTechnique : encre (techniques dessin)\r\nTechnique : peinture \u00e0 l\u0027eau (techniques peinture)","placeOfCreation":"","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Collection Adolphe Thiers; legs Elise Dosne Thiers, 1880, suivant les volont\u00e9s de son mari Adolphe Thiers et sous r\u00e9serve d\u2019usufruit de sa s\u0153ur F\u00e9licie Dosne qui y renonce et ex\u00e9cute le legs en 1881.","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"Mme Dosne-Thiers, Elise","note":"","role":", Donateur"},{"value":"M. Thiers, Louis Adolphe","note":"","role":", Collectionneur"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"legs sous r\u00e9serve d\u0027usufruit","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date d\u0027arriv\u00e9e au Mus\u00e9e","value":"1881","startYear":1881,"endYear":1881}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","longTermLoanTo":"","index":{"Mode d\u0027acquisi